<div class="bg"                 style="background-color: #ebebeb;
                                margin: 0;
                                font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';
                                font-size: 1rem;
                                font-weight: 400;
                                line-height: 1.5;
                                color: #212529;
                                text-align: left;">
  <center>
    <div class="card"           style="width: 50%;
                                background-color: white;
                                border-style: solid;
                                border-color: #ebebeb;
                                border-width: 20px;
                                -moz-box-shadow: inset 0 0 2px #6f6f6f;
                                -webkit-box-shadow: inset 0 0 2px #6f6f6f;
                                box-shadow: inset 0 0 2px #6f6f6f;">
      <div class="logo-banner"  style="height: auto;
                                display: flex;
                                background-color: #64ba69;">
        <h2 class="logo"        style="margin: 3%;
                                font-weight: 500;">BuchaBuddy</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="intent-banner"style="background-color: #96ed98;
                                padding: 15px;">
        <h4                     style="margin: 0px;
                                font-weight: 500;">Password Change Notification</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="">
        <p>Hey <%= @resource.email %>!</p>

        <p>You asked us to reset your password. You can do this by clicking the button below.</p>

        <p>
          <%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token),
                                style: "color: #fff;
                                background-color: #31893d;
                                border-color: #31893d;
                                -moz-appearance: button;
                                appearance: button;
                                text-decoration: none;
                                display: inline-block;
                                font-weight: 400;
                                text-align: center;
                                white-space: nowrap;
                                vertical-align: middle;
                                -webkit-user-select: none;
                                -moz-user-select: none;
                                -ms-user-select: none;
                                user-select: none;
                                border: 1px solid transparent;
                                padding: 0.375rem 0.75rem;
                                font-size: 1rem;
                                line-height: 1.5;
                                border-radius: 0.25rem;
                                margin-top: 12px;" %>
        </p>
        <p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
        <p>Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>
        <p                      style="font-size: 0.8rem;
                                margin: 30px;">
          This account email has been sent to you as part of your BuchaBuddy membership.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card"           style="width: 47.5%;
                                background-color: white;
                                border-style: solid;
                                border-color: #ebebeb;
                                border-width: 20px;
                                -moz-box-shadow: inset 0 0 2px #6f6f6f;
                                -webkit-box-shadow: inset 0 0 2px #6f6f6f;
                                box-shadow: inset 0 0 2px #6f6f6f;
                                padding: 19px;">
      <div class="open-source"  style="background-color: #96ed98;
                                padding: 15px;">
        <h5                     style="margin: 0px;">Help Our Cultures Grow!</h5>
      </div>
      <p                        style="font-size: 0.8rem;">
        BuchaBuddy is an open source web application made with ❤️ for all the Kombucha homebrewers around the world. This software would not be possible without the care and attention of the open source community.
      </p>
      <p                        style="font-size: 0.8rem;">
        We are always looking for help developing new features and maintaining existing ones. Check us out on <a href="https://github.com/buchabuddy/buchabuddy/tree/master" target="_blank">GitHub</a> to contribute.
      </p>
      <a href="https://github.com/buchabuddy/buchabuddy/tree/master" target="_blank">
        <img src="https://assets-cdn.github.com/images/modules/logos_page/GitHub-Mark.png" alt="octocat-logo" style="width: 10%;">
      </a>
    </div>

    <p style="font-size: 0.8rem;
       padding-bottom: 20px;
       color: #6f6f6f;">
      Please do not reply to this email, as we are unable to respond from this email address.<br>This message was mailed to [<%= @email %>] by BuchaBuddy.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 0.8rem;
       padding-bottom: 20px;
       color: #6f6f6f;">
      <a href="https://github.com/buchabuddy/buchabuddy/tree/master" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;">Source Code</a> and <a href="http://buchabuddy.com" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;">Website</a> by BuchaBuddy<br>
      © 2018 All Rights Reserved.<br>
      Denver, Colorado 80202
    </p>
  </center>
</div>
